      protected void AbstractMetric.sendTriples(java.util.Properties results, java.util.Set<java.lang.String> isResource, java.util.Properties recv, Triple[] add)
      Will call the storageManager sendData method with the Lightweight Meta and the following created triples
      The triples add will be simply added
      The subject node will be calculated from the recv Object wiht the AbstractMetric.getSubjectFromExtraMeta(java.util.Properties) Method

      For each key:value pair: subject results.key results.value
      Be aware that the Set isResource will set if the key/value will be handled as resources.
      protected void AbstractMetric.sendTriples(java.lang.String subject, java.util.Properties results, java.util.Set<java.lang.String> isResource, java.util.Properties recv, Triple[] add)
      Will call the storageManager sendData method with the Lightweight Meta and the following created triples
      The triples add will be simply added
      The subject node will be the subject for every following triple

      For each key:value pair: subject results.key results.value
      Be aware that the Set isResource will set if the key/value will be handled as resources.
